{"tid":416933,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"路試油塘定天光道難？","createTime":"2017-09-28T08:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T14:07:21.000Z","uid":89403,"like":37,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"009461ad9e8e0630c329e144f1cd887ac2d2c293","tid":416933,"uid":89403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n自己考天光道，但係聽講油塘好難考，想聽下人分享下心得<br />\n<br />\n油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天光道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c1253ae8e32f286ddfdcfd26b4039e0cbd6c52","tid":416933,"uid":61766,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"無考過，但自己住油塘，路已經唔易，再加上勁多阿伯阿婆以為自己係貓有九條命，亂過馬路"},{"pid":"5090d9e4600fd72ec4f6795b44a5b7302aebd11a","tid":416933,"uid":89403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無考過，但自己住油塘，路已經唔易，再加上勁多阿伯阿婆以為自己係貓有九條命，亂過馬路</blockquote><br />\nd上左年紀嘅以為舉起隻手就一定要讓你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4b46372419bbd9b9482cfd80b2f40d07501405","tid":416933,"uid":60622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"考油塘嘅話提前多啲練習斜路操作迴旋處操作就得 無乜其他地形"},{"pid":"402b5dad17d151f444e41e7bd758ac06a81ba7f9","tid":416933,"uid":126312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無考過，但自己住油塘，路已經唔易，再加上勁多阿伯阿婆以為自己係貓有九條命，亂過馬路</blockquote><br />\nd上左年紀嘅以為舉起隻手就一定要讓你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舉起手咪叫正常少少. 學車個陣次次都有阿伯望都唔望直行直過"},{"pid":"e0e98640e17edb8453b460f09b122d526ad48ce5","tid":416933,"uid":92036,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"忠義街短線最難"},{"pid":"95e11c073284c90b4981d2439418184628b77d5f","tid":416933,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"最難山光道，其他無視"},{"pid":"d157328d1fd530d79179d2b0f34decddb7e89d8e","tid":416933,"uid":62243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"我考油塘<br />\n覺得最煩係個迴旋處"},{"pid":"d60cdcaefe0ede44c5ef996713993025dd6b8616","tid":416933,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"第一次天光道考，岩岩學生午飯完返晒學校既時間，路路暢通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dcda71702a1f2c6f9909995aac8229d7047d57","tid":416933,"uid":89403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忠義街短線最難</blockquote><br />\n有無得詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f019f83367c974a9d4cc3301b45109164ebb39e9","tid":416933,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最難山光道，其他無視</blockquote><br />\n認同"},{"pid":"6fc9d79e36083ec6072a22968e6fea2dc85ce9cd","tid":416933,"uid":89403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次天光道考，岩岩學生午飯完返晒學校既時間，路路暢通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天光道考，好彩落完雨條街少左人，1 take pass，一天都光哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8740c169e7579d598888a510a8a2c479f4a053e3","tid":416933,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無考過，但自己住油塘，路已經唔易，再加上勁多阿伯阿婆以為自己係貓有九條命，亂過馬路</blockquote><br />\nd上左年紀嘅以為舉起隻手就一定要讓你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舉起手咪叫正常少少. 學車個陣次次都有阿伯望都唔望直行直過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係，係油塘中心嗰條馬路又無紅綠燈又無黃波燈，望住架巴士呀大貨van駛緊埋黎，繼續衝，真係一覺唔留神可以車死幾件"},{"pid":"7e67aee24e68a1e5885b0d936004f3734958b10f","tid":416933,"uid":107078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7839a35bc1ca405c43abe69d61937b263371b649","tid":416933,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>忠義街短線最難</blockquote><br />\n有無得詳細少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺忠義街難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難在條線窄<br />\n但肯定既唔會係最難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbad5b5fb596251f88a66ef5c324f1af912e7a1f","tid":416933,"uid":88711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:44:13.000Z","msg":"一定係天光道 死車多到仆街"},{"pid":"f2695366be710dc5b1ade3141095844e57d4bb81","tid":416933,"uid":1538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:45:47.000Z","msg":"考左兩次<br />\n天光道fail<br />\n油塘pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9097908b15842b088b46f1ad9d04c1e18194c2","tid":416933,"uid":20101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:24:26.000Z","msg":"肥天光道<br />\n油塘pass<br />\n<br />\n天光道多斜 路窄 路邊車多 學生多  渣棍吊極力子比較麻煩<br />\n<br />\n油塘條路感覺上 比較寛少少 車流量無咁多 <br />\n伏位係迴旋處 同 有條路要水泥廠係附近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0696eee7c921407614bfda02c14099e78c8e339","tid":416933,"uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"考兩次天光道先pass<br />\n基本上無學生時間就好易"},{"pid":"7834ec1cf2a9daed828114d29944462da55dc495","tid":416933,"uid":66195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"油唐多貨車 路口好難望有沒車"},{"pid":"e3f6555b726474a8ab32aa65f5bcb468d890c509","tid":416933,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忠義街短線最難</blockquote><br />\n上年尾1take<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3a0ab1947b8ffe0a817aea43976b25012b9550","tid":416933,"uid":64850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"兩個都考過 睇路線。<br />\n<br />\n油塘既路線難度比較平均，難係難在迴旋處，但其實唔心急慢慢睇清楚再出就可以。（到親迴旋處我老閪都停定先，入定波等隨時準備開車。我自己衰另一樣on9野，柒左，搞到一個Serious肥左）<br />\n天光道既路線黎講靠背壟道最難，難度一定係油塘之上，路窄多死車，多人橫過馬路，甚至係馬路上分隔線行既人都有，無得練考即場反應同睇你好唔好彩（我練車果陣成日有菲傭同廢老係死車後衝出黎，麻撚煩）。總之呢條路線大把位可以肥你。另兩條線係公主道同亞皆老街，無乜特別都係幾易考。<br />\n<br />\n總結：靠背壟道(天光道)&gt;油塘&gt;公主道(天光道)&gt;亞皆老街(天光道)"},{"pid":"5a1e5cf7afd1d1ba5c5e208733ad2ebc69707b7a","tid":416933,"uid":592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"油塘頭兩個彎位冇出事就合格硬咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9adeba2a12cb318becff2fd41f985037d5874f","tid":416933,"uid":107444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:08:01.000Z","msg":"掃杆蒲又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b7c0090d97d57a05ec063496794b2c8b85c8a1","tid":416933,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"油塘1 take pass <br />\n最緊要迴旋處小心 <br />\n同埋啊婆衝出黎<br />\n我考個時係巴士站條斜路都有啊婆衝出黎 <br />\nDup完再起步 但無拉手制 就咁吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都合格"}]}